    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123100/extras/fab83fdc2b5be0dc975a9d62c1ebe4df.avif?t=1745226063\" width=650 height=180 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>游戏类型：猫险解咪游戏。<br>你，一只黑色小猫咪，需要在神秘岛屿中边冒险边解开古代遗迹的机关谜题。<br></li><li>开发团队：猫咪岛施工队</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123100/extras/b81a5abec3883105c2597c888b6a314d.avif?t=1745226063\" width=650 height=180 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 美术风格清新可爱，主角是扁扁的黑色猫猫和白色猫猫头包。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123100/extras/c2b782646ae3c529ecf29a5717940b4a.poster.avif?t=1745226063\" width=650 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123100/extras/c2b782646ae3c529ecf29a5717940b4a.webm?t=1745226063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123100/extras/c2b782646ae3c529ecf29a5717940b4a.mp4?t=1745226063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123100/extras/4887545c71587d56be7a22929bc2da55.avif?t=1745226063\" width=650 height=180 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 对于小猫咪来说辽阔的地图，能够满足爱冒险的小猫咪的探索欲。<br></li><li>岛屿会给予小猫咪丰富且可爱的交互反馈。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123100/extras/097ef1a0a0477e47a20fe6e8231993c6.poster.avif?t=1745226063\" width=650 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123100/extras/097ef1a0a0477e47a20fe6e8231993c6.webm?t=1745226063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123100/extras/097ef1a0a0477e47a20fe6e8231993c6.mp4?t=1745226063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123100/extras/e129189ea4b544b79ab2463fe319fc58.avif?t=1745226063\" width=650 height=180 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 剧情和对话风格轻松搞怪。<br></li><li>我们的主角——一只从天而降到神秘小岛的黑色小猫咪，找到丢失的白色猫猫头背包后踏上了收集电池并回到火箭的旅途。<br>猫咪和背包从海滨平原出发并沿路收集贝壳，解决了电车站的麻烦后坐上电车通往岛另一边的上山路。<br>来到群岛镇后，帮助镇民们恢复因为特殊原因暂停的庆典。庆典恢复后，猫咪和背包通过奇妙的途径来到火箭所在的雪山。<br>雪山上，猫咪和背包因为厚厚的积雪步履维艰，但在火箭研究员们和指引路牌的帮助下，猫咪最终踩着一串串脚印回到了火箭，可喜可贺！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123100/extras/feec05ff10935f1c9054736dc17a553e.avif?t=1745226063\" width=650 height=180 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>我们是一个学生团队，《喵之旅人》是我们的毕业作品。<br>主策陆睢：首先，让我来喵几句：喵喵喵喵喵！（总算做完啦！）<br>主程 &amp; 技术美术 Bot：喵喵喵喵喵。（感觉头秃了。）<br>美术 &amp; 地编：Yume：喵喵喵喵喵！（大家辛苦啦！）<br>移植Laplace：喵喵喵喵喵~（希望人没事~）<br>策划炒饭阿叔：喵喵喵喵喵？（可以解放啦？）<br>音效川一：喵喵！（好耶！）<br>关卡做作业：喵喵喵喵喵喵喵！（喵天堂天下第一！）<br>最后祝所有玩家都能享受和猫猫的春游，希望大家会喜欢我们的小猫咪和包包！<br>（下图仅为开发团队对您美好喵生的祝贺，非游戏实机画面）</li></ul> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123100/extras/97f124ad8d397db5e54428b5e5640fdf.poster.avif?t=1745226063\" width=650 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123100/extras/97f124ad8d397db5e54428b5e5640fdf.webm?t=1745226063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2123100/extras/97f124ad8d397db5e54428b5e5640fdf.mp4?t=1745226063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
